cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.NE 

The paper discusses reinforcement learning algorithms and their performance in different environments. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of these algorithms in robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper proposes the use of neural networks (cs.NE) to detect and adapt to different meta-features of environments.
